headline: WM Announces Cash Dividend
summary: HOUSTON, November 14, 2024--WM (NYSE: WM) today announced the declaration of a quarterly cash dividend of $0.75 per share payable Dec. 20, 2024, to stockholders of record on Dec. 6, 2024.

headline: Nvidia, Walmart, Target report earnings: Yahoo Finance
summary: The week of November 18 is going to be filled with big-name earnings reports. The biggest is Nvidia, which releases its fiscal third quarter results after the market close on Wednesday, November 20. Also reporting that day, but before the bell, is Target. Investors will also hear from Walmart on November 19 and Gap on November 21.
